OL,3,CCompletion date confirmed for Heads of
OL,4,Cthe Valleys road
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has announced
OL,7,Fwhen current work on the Heads of the
OL,8,FValleys road, a road development
OL,9,Fproject that has been a number of
OL,10,Fyears in the making, will finish.
OL,12,FWork on the current section, Dowlais
OL,13,Fto Hirwaun, started in 2021 and the
OL,14,Fproject is estimated to cost more than
OL,15,Fa billion pounds to complete but it is
OL,16,Fdue to be finished by summer 2025.
