OL,3,CCompletion date confirmed for Heads of
OL,4,Cthe Valleys road
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government said the project
OL,7,Fwill improve accessibility, reduce
OL,8,Fjourney times, provide extra
OL,9,Fresilience and reliability and enhance
OL,10,Froad safety.
OL,12,FIt says the A465 (Hirwaun to Dowlais)
OL,13,Fproject when completed later this year
OL,14,Fwill have delivered 17.7km of new dual
OL,15,Fcarriageway, 6.1km of sideroads, more
OL,16,Fthan 14km of active travel routes 30
OL,17,Fnew bridges and 28 retaining walls.
