OL,3,CCompletion date confirmed for Heads of
OL,4,Cthe Valleys road
OL,6,FAs well as connecting communities by
OL,7,Flinking the Valleys, South and West
OL,8,FWales to the English Midlands and
OL,9,Fbeyond, the Welsh Government says the
OL,10,Fscheme has also created significant
OL,11,Fopportunities for the local economy.
OL,13,FIt said more than 2,000 new jobs have
OL,14,Fbeen created, with more than half of
OL,15,Fthose employed living locally, and
OL,16,Falso employed 158 apprentices.
