OL,3,CCompletion date confirmed for Heads of
OL,4,Cthe Valleys road
OL,6,FTo mitigate the ecological impacts of
OL,7,Fthe road building, the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment said a number of measures
OL,9,Fwere taken like the relocation of
OL,10,Fspecies such as great crested newt and
OL,11,Fmarsh fritillary butterfly.
OL,13,FBut the scheme's been controversial in
OL,14,Fsome areas with residents complaining
OL,15,Fabout the disruption. Some claim
OL,16,Fdamage has been caused to their homes
OL,17,Fby vibrations of the works while
OL,18,Fothers say the noise has been a
OL,19,Fconstant frustration.
