OL,3,CCompletion date confirmed for Heads of
OL,4,Cthe Valleys road
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives have welcomed
OL,7,Fthe news of completion of an
OL,8,Finfrastructure project but said people
OL,9,Fwould be right to question whether the
OL,10,Fcost of the project, was worth it.
OL,12,FWelsh Conservative Shadow Cabinet
OL,13,FSecretary for Transport and
OL,14,FInfrastructure, Peter Fox MS said:
OL,15,F"This overbudget and well behind
OL,16,Fschedule project epitomises Labour's
OL,17,F25 years of failure here in Wales.
