OL,6,F"By scrapping many other vital
OL,7,Finfrastructure projects like the much-
OL,8,Fneeded M4 relief road, the cost of
OL,9,Fwhich would have nearly been covered
OL,10,Fby the Heads of the Valleys price tag,
OL,11,Fthe Welsh public will rightly question
OL,12,Fwhether this gargantuan expense was
OL,13,Fworth it."
